{"id":1232,"date":"2022-02-20T11:33:08","date_gmt":"2022-02-20T11:33:08","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/?p=1232"},"modified":"2022-02-20T11:33:13","modified_gmt":"2022-02-20T11:33:13","slug":"configure-ipv4-and-ipv6-addresses","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/?p=1232","title":{"rendered":"Configure IPv4 and IPv6 addresses"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>This should be a really straight forward guide, you all probably know what is an IP address or what&#8217;s the difference between IPv4 and IPv6, but If not I&#8217;ll make a short refresh of your memory.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>An\u00a0<strong>IP (Internet Protocol) address<\/strong>\u00a0is a numerical label assigned to each device connected to a\u00a0computer network\u00a0that uses the IP protocol for communication. An IP address acts as an identifier for a specific device on a particular network<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>IPv4\u00a0and\u00a0IPv6\u00a0are internet protocol version 4 and internet protocol version 6, IP version 6 is the new version of Internet Protocol, which is way better than IP version 4 in terms of complexity and efficiency.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"121\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-149.png?resize=640%2C121&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1235\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-149.png?w=959&amp;ssl=1 959w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-149.png?resize=300%2C57&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-149.png?resize=768%2C145&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-149.png?resize=24%2C5&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-149.png?resize=36%2C7&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-149.png?resize=48%2C9&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"how-to-configure-ipv4\">How to configure IPv4<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>As always with Linux, there are many ways to do this. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Using GUI<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is very simple and user-friendly as the only thing you need to type is an actual IP. First open settings go to network <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"444\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-150.png?resize=640%2C444&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1236\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-150.png?w=989&amp;ssl=1 989w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-150.png?resize=300%2C208&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-150.png?resize=768%2C533&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-150.png?resize=24%2C17&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-150.png?resize=36%2C25&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-150.png?resize=48%2C33&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Then you click on the wheel icon in wired category.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"486\" height=\"98\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-151.png?resize=486%2C98&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1237\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-151.png?w=486&amp;ssl=1 486w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-151.png?resize=300%2C60&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-151.png?resize=24%2C5&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-151.png?resize=36%2C7&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-151.png?resize=48%2C10&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 486px) 100vw, 486px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Go to IPv4\/IPv6 category and change the method to manual.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"574\" height=\"529\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-152.png?resize=574%2C529&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1238\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-152.png?w=574&amp;ssl=1 574w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-152.png?resize=300%2C276&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-152.png?resize=24%2C22&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-152.png?resize=36%2C33&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-152.png?resize=48%2C44&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 574px) 100vw, 574px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Using nmui<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another way of changing the IP address is using a tool called nmui which is used in CLI which is most commonly used in production environment. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">nmtui<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>You are then prompted by simple GUI like interface.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-153.png?resize=640%2C428&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1239\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-153.png?w=735&amp;ssl=1 735w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-153.png?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-153.png?resize=24%2C16&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-153.png?resize=36%2C24&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-153.png?resize=48%2C32&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To change the IP go to &#8220;Edit connection&#8221; and choose your interface connection (most likely Ethernet)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-154.png?resize=300%2C150&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1240\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-154.png?w=300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-154.png?resize=24%2C12&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-154.png?resize=36%2C18&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-154.png?resize=48%2C24&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Choose &#8220;edit&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"274\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-155.png?resize=640%2C274&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1241\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-155.png?w=663&amp;ssl=1 663w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-155.png?resize=300%2C129&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-155.png?resize=24%2C10&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-155.png?resize=36%2C15&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-155.png?resize=48%2C21&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>And finally, choose IPv4\/IPv6 CONFIGURATION and change &#8220;automatic&#8221; to &#8220;manual&#8221;.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"248\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-156.png?resize=640%2C248&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1242\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-156.png?w=698&amp;ssl=1 698w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-156.png?resize=300%2C116&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-156.png?resize=24%2C9&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-156.png?resize=36%2C14&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-156.png?resize=48%2C19&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Rewriting the network scripts\/ifcfg-* textfile<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Because everything in the Linux is a file, this as well can be change by just rewriting the text file which works perfectly fine as well and probably many people even prefer this method.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">vi \/etc\/sysconfig\/network-scripts\/ifcfg-*<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"437\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-157.png?resize=640%2C437&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1243\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-157.png?w=736&amp;ssl=1 736w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-157.png?resize=300%2C205&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-157.png?resize=24%2C16&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-157.png?resize=36%2C25&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-157.png?resize=48%2C33&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>To apply the changes, restart the service<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">service network restart<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>This should be a really straight forward guide, you all probably know what is an [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1246,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"nf_dc_page":"","om_disable_all_campaigns":false,"_mi_skip_tracking":false},"categories":[219],"tags":[100,34,446,447,220],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/rhsa-Manage-basic-networking.png?fit=1280%2C720&ssl=1","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1232"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fcomments&post=1232"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1232\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1247,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1232\/revisions\/1247"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/media\/1246"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fmedia&parent=1232"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fcategories&post=1232"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Ftags&post=1232"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}